An '''aircart''' was a form of mobility technology that was employed by the [[Yevetha]]. One was used aboard the [[Aramadia (Aramadia-class)|''Aramadia'']], where it was used to carry [[Nil Spaar]] up eleven levels to the domain of [[Vor Duull]], the proctor of information science for the ship.

